    "Departures": "Bottom line of a CFD. Cumulative count of items that have exited the workflow (last state) by each sample date. Slope = throughput.",
    "WIP": "Work In Progress. Vertical distance between two adjacent CFD lines at a sample date = items currently in that workflow band. Per (see DECISIONS.md for the math).",
